    <div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system clearfix">

    
  <div class="content">
    <article id="node-17" class="node node-page clearfix">

  
  <div class="content">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>The Open Source Initiative is overseen and managed by an eleven-person Board of Directors. The current Board comprises the following individuals (in alphabetical order):</p>

